</p></section><section id="GUID-1156E15C-FA11-42F7-80CE-F9823F371FA9" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Function</title><p class="- topic/p "> Use this test to set the ink tube status to empty. For instance if you replace an ink tube. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> This is the initial situation for a brand new system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> This setting will increase the ink dosing timeout so that the tube and the printhead fill with ink. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Status is automatically updated after successful ink filling. 
</p></section><section id="GUID-92369981-F020-4E62-9707-58F93D054214" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Values</title><p class="- topic/p ">To mark an ink tube empty enter 1. 
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-A88E4D10-AA7C-455F-861B-33C950A4AD64" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> Do not change this setting in combination with filled printheads. 
</p></note><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Minimum value: 0 
